<file path="README.md">
# Astro Starter Kit: Basics

```sh
npm create astro@latest -- --template basics
```

> 🧑‍🚀 **Seasoned astronaut?** Delete this file. Have fun!

## 🚀 Project Structure

Inside of your Astro project, you'll see the following folders and files:

```text
/
├── public/
│   └── favicon.svg
├── src
│   ├── assets
│   │   └── astro.svg
│   ├── components
│   │   └── Welcome.astro
│   ├── layouts
│   │   └── Layout.astro
│   └── pages
│       └── index.astro
└── package.json
```

To learn more about the folder structure of an Astro project, refer to [our guide on project structure](https://docs.astro.build/en/basics/project-structure/).

## 🧞 Commands

All commands are run from the root of the project, from a terminal:

| Command                   | Action                                           |
| :------------------------ | :----------------------------------------------- |
| `npm install`             | Installs dependencies                            |
| `npm run dev`             | Starts local dev server at `localhost:4321`      |
| `npm run build`           | Build your production site to `./dist/`          |
| `npm run preview`         | Preview your build locally, before deploying     |
| `npm run astro ...`       | Run CLI commands like `astro add`, `astro check` |
| `npm run astro -- --help` | Get help using the Astro CLI                     |

## 👀 Want to learn more?

Feel free to check [our documentation](https://docs.astro.build) or jump into our [Discord server](https://astro.build/chat).
</file>

<file path="src/components/ContactFormSection.astro">
---
// Fichier : src/components/ContactFormSection.astro
import Container from './Container.astro';

// Hostinger Mailer / Formspree Configuration
// REMPLACER 'VOTRE_ID_FORMSPREE' par votre ID réel
const formAction = "https://formspree.io/f/VOTRE_ID_FORMSPREE"; 
const successRedirect = "/merci"; // Redirection après succès (si nécessaire)
---

<section id="contact-form-section" class="py-7xl">
    <Container class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-7xl">
        
        {/* 1. Bloc du Formulaire de Contact */}
        <div class="col-span-1">
            
            {/* Titres */}
            <div class="mb-xxl space-y-sm">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-text-body-primary">Quick Contact</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-text-body-secondary">Laissez-moi un message :)</p>
            </div>
            
            {/* Formulaire */}
            <form id="contact-form" action={formAction} method="POST" class="space-y-md">
                
                {/* Champ Sujet */}
                <input 
                    name="subject" 
                    type="text" 
                    class="w-full p-md bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-stroke-secondary text-text-body-primary placeholder:text-text-body-tertiary focus:border-text-brand focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none transition duration-200"
                    placeholder="Sujet du message"
                    required
                />
                
                {/* Nom et Prénom */}
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-md">
                    <input 
                        name="firstName" 
                        type="text" 
                        class="w-full p-md bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-stroke-secondary text-text-body-primary placeholder:text-text-body-tertiary focus:border-text-brand focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none transition duration-200"
                        placeholder="Prénom" 
                        required
                    />
                    <input 
                        name="lastName" 
                        type="text" 
                        class="w-full p-md bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-stroke-secondary text-text-body-primary placeholder:text-text-body-tertiary focus:border-text-brand focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none transition duration-200"
                        placeholder="Nom" 
                        required
                    />
                </div>
                
                {/* Champ Email */}
                <input 
                    name="email" 
                    type="email" 
                    name="_replyto" 
                    class="w-full p-md bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-stroke-secondary text-text-body-primary placeholder:text-text-body-tertiary focus:border-text-brand focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none transition duration-200"
                    placeholder="Votre email" 
                    required
                />
                
                {/* Champ Message */}
                <textarea 
                    name="message" 
                    class="w-full p-md bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-stroke-secondary text-text-body-primary placeholder:text-text-body-tertiary focus:border-text-brand focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none transition duration-200" 
                    rows="5" 
                    placeholder="Votre message"
                    required
                ></textarea>
                
                {/* Champs cachés pour Formspree */}
                <input type="hidden" name="_next" value={`https://votredomaine.com${successRedirect}`} />
                <input type="text" name="_gotcha" class="hidden" /> 
                
                {/* Bouton de Soumission */}
                <button 
                    type="submit" 
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto mt-sm px-xl py-md bg-text-brand text-background-primary font-bold uppercase rounded-sm hover:bg-opacity-80 transition duration-200"
                >
                    Envoyer le message
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        {/* 2. Bloc d'informations de contact (Adapté de l'ancien footer) */}
        <div class="col-span-1 text-text-body-secondary flex flex-col justify-start space-y-md pt-xxl md:pt-3xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-body-primary">Contact Direct</h3>
            <p>Yassine El Idrissi <br> **contact@yassineelidrissi.com**</p>
            
            {/* L'icône SVG décorative peut être réinsérée ici si vous le souhaitez,
                mais je ne l'ai pas incluse pour l'instant pour garder le design moderne. */}
                
            <p class="text-sm text-text-body-tertiary pt-xl">
                 Designed by Yassine El Idrissi
            </p>
        </div>

    </Container>
</section>
</file>

